section.section:
A plan developed under paragraph (1) of this subsection shall include:
A description of the way the institution addresses cultural diversity among its student, faculty, and staff populations;
A description of how the institution plans to enhance cultural diversity, if improvement is needed;
A process for reporting campus-based hate crimes, as defined under Title 10, Subtitle 3 of the Criminal Law Article and consistent with federal requirements under 20 U.S.C. 1092(f), known as the Jeanne Clery Disclosure of Campus Security Policy and Campus Crime Statistics Act; and
A summary of any resources, including State grants, needed by the institution to effectively recruit and retain a culturally diverse student body.
